<template>
	<trend
		:data="speeds"
		:gradientDirection="top"
		:gradient="['#6fa8dc', '#42b983', '#2c3e50']"
		:padding="8"
		:radius="8"
		:stroke-width="1"
		:stroke-linecap="butt"
		auto-draw
		height="200"
	>
	</trend>
</template>

<script>
import Trend from  "vuetrend"
import _ from 'underscore'


export default {
    name: 'HorseExtraView',
    components: {
		Trend
    },
    props : ['horse'],
    data () {
		return {
			
        }
    },
	computed : {
		speeds () {
			return _.pluck(this.horse.pastPerformances, "brisspeedRating"); 
		}
	},
    methods : {


    }
}
</script>
